race.comment: CAVILL TYCOON (2) led them up last start at this track and held on for the win first-up, scoring by 0.2L. He was the favourite there and he looks to have taken a liking to the WA climate following a stable switch. Can build on what he did fresh and bring up back-to-back wins. HYPERREAL (3) bolted in by 2.4L here to break his maiden at start 22. That is the query, though he was right back in grade there after some solid showings in town. Drops back in trip today for Faithfull and he can feature once again. INSYDE SUCCESS (1) brings in some very strong first-up form, missing by 1.5L in Saturday grade when fresh last campaign. His latest trial here was very strong and while he hasn't won for a while, this looks a very suitable race to end the drought. ASURIITO (5) makes his WA debut today and comes here without a trial. Had shown some ability in NSW and is not to be discounted. PURO (4) can feature first-up with a trial under her belt.
